hopobject.body: I'd like to apply for this job culchethhealth.co.uk The device is powered by an Exynos 5 Octa processor, 2GB of RAM, has an 8MP camera, a 2,400 mAh battery, and offers anywhere from 16 to 128GB of memory. All of this fits into a 9.1mm thick frame. It’s pretty impressive what they did with memory, because most phones don’t offer more than 32GB. With a 128GB device, I definitely wouldn’t mind not having a microSD slot. Top that off with a high end Wolfson audio chip and you have a very high end phone.
